Statusd is a reimagining of Seend script designed to track users by storing thier latest activity & hostmask. Activities include joined, parted, kicked, quit, nick change, and action. If name specified is not found a pattern search will be performed instead and results displayed. Script also includes the ability to search for nicks by hostmask using the host parameter. As well as an automatic backup system that saves on .die, restart, timed intervals, and by backup trigger.
